{
  "stem": "26585.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They came from Africa-- Rommel had lost.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were all going, heim ins reich, back home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he came and said, follow me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Followed him, and he was looking and looking, and one of the cars had a little sign that said [GERMAN] one warden, three prisoners.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We went up, and the soldiers went, ah, Fraulein, Fraulein.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we looked at him, and he said [POINTING] And we walked in there, and that compartment was full of soldiers.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But on one side-- there were wooden benches-- on one side there was that sign again, one warden, three prisoners.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we sat down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We knew that was us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And across from us were all these German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when we sat down, they burst out laughing, and laughed, and laughed, and said, leave it to our German women.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They will think of anything to get back home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They thought we dreamt this-- because you see, all the Germans, or the German generation of Germans, knew what was happening, and they wanted to get back.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You couldn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The trains were soldiers-- that's all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they knew that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so they thought, our German women, how smart they are.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And this is their friend, and that's how they'll get.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they talked to us like we were, you know-- the gestapo guy did not open his mouth.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only rumors we heard in Ruma, from, through the grapevine, is that the British are coming from the south, and the Russians are coming from here, and Germany has lost the war.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, jewelry she had.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, sure, we lived on that for a long time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The German soldiers shared their food and their water with us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the guy didn't open his mouth.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
